&#x02013;8]</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Comorbidities, no. (%)</td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;&#x02003;&#x02003;Current smokers,</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">11(28)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">4(29)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">4(36)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">3(30)</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;&#x02003;&#x02003;Chronic alcohol abuse</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">8(20)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">3(21)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">2(18)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">2(20)</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;&#x02003;&#x02003;Obesity</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">8(20)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">2(14)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">4(36)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">2(20)</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;&#x02003;&#x02003;Coronary artery disease</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">4(10)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">1(7)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">3(30)</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;&#x02003;&#x02003;Hypertensive heart disease</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">15(38)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">4(29)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">4(36)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">5(50)</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;&#x02003;&#x02003;Congestive heart disease</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">2(5)</td><td align="center" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0</td><td alig